behind his back.

20
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:27,839
- How did he find out ?
- Well, I told him. Y'know...

21
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:30,440
You... You told me to tell him.

22
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:33,600
You said it would clear the air, you know.

23
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,556
