198
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,239
Come on, Colin,
we're taking you away from this place !

199
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:13,840
- Colin ?
- That's what I called my box.

200
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:30,270
Hi, Dom, yeah. This is Duane Benzie.

201
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:34,677
